title: The part-time model with a Youth Olympic silver medal and more from Lausanne 2020
description: Gu Ailing Eileen of China is a freestyle skier with a Youth Olympic silver medal and went to Paris Fashion Week in her spare time. We also catch up with Estonia's Kelly Sildaru who won the slopestyle freestyle skiing. Plus, two-time Olympic champion curler John Morris gives some tips on how to calm your nerves.
